description: Canadian book and magazine illustrator who co-pencilled and inked for Dark Horse comics the X-wing Marks the Spot and Imperial Spy story arcs with Ken Steacy for Star Wars Kids magazine, reprinted in Star Wars Omnibus: Wild Space. He also assisted Ken Steacy with penciling, inking, lettering and coloring on the Dark Horse web comic Podracing Tales as well as numerous Star Wars children's books for Random House and Golden Books, among others. In 2012 he illustrated the fundraising comic book style book "Hero Up!" for Rodale.

deck: Jeff Bridges is an Oscar-winning actor, accomplished country musician, and producer.
description:
Comic Related Roles

Obadiah Stane

In the critically adored 2008 film, Iron Man, Bridges starred alongside Robert Downey Jr., Gwyneth Paltrow, and Terrence Howard. He played the villainous role of long-time Iron Man villain Obadiah Stane, the Iron Monger.This film marked the first time Iron Man had been brought to the big screen and laid the foundation for the Marvel Cinematic Universe.

Roy Pulsipher

In the 2013 movie, R.I.P.D., an adaptation of the Dark Horse Comics series of the same name, Bridges costarred alongside Ryan Reynolds as R.I.P.D. officer Roy Pulsipher.

Kingsman: The Golden Circle

Jeff Bridges is set to play an as of yet unnamed character in the sequel to Matthew Vaughn's Kingsman: The Secret Service.
name: Jeff Bridges
